@Trailblazers.Backend_HostAddress = http://localhost:5011

### Submit a Contact Form
POST {{Trailblazers.Backend_HostAddress}}/api/submissions/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "email": "janedoe@example.com",
  "message": "Hello, I am interested in partnering with Trailblazers. Please let me know the best time to connect."
}

### Submit a Student Registration
POST {{Trailblazers.Backend_HostAddress}}/api/submissions/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alex Smith",
  "email": "alex.smith@example.com",
  "phoneNumber": "+1234567890",
  "targetExam": "JAMB"
}

### Get Submissions (Unauthorized)
GET {{Trailblazers.Backend_HostAddress}}/api/submissions
Accept: application/json

### Get Submissions (Authorized - Contacts)
GET {{Trailblazers.Backend_HostAddress}}/api/submissions?type=0&pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
X-API-KEY: trailblazers-secret-key
Accept: application/json

### Get Submissions (Authorized - Registrations)
GET {{Trailblazers.Backend_HostAddress}}/api/submissions?type=1&pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
X-API-KEY: trailblazers-secret-key
Accept: application/json
